## 🌐 GitHub Workflow

### 🔹 Pull Request (PR) Flow

1. Create feature branch
2. Make changes and commit
3. Push to remote repository
4. Create Pull Request
5. Code review process
6. CI checks (build + test)
7. Merge to main branch

