## 🔄 Fork vs Clone

| Feature | Fork                             | Clone                     |
| ------- | -------------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| Purpose | Copy repo to your GitHub account | Copy repo to local system |
| Usage   | Open-source contributions        | Team collaboration        |

