## ⚙️ CI/CD Overview

### 🔹 CI (Continuous Integration)

* Automatically builds code
* Runs tests
* Ensures code quality

### 🔹 CD (Continuous Deployment)

* Deploys code to:

  * Staging
  * Production
* Often automated after merge

